# Personal research knowledgebase — contains unpublished ideas, grant strategy,
# and active project details. Kept local only; CI restores it from the
# KB_CONTENT GitHub Secret before running the pipeline. See README.md.
data/knowledgebase.md

# LLM rerank cache — stores per-paper score AND a one-sentence reason. The
# reason is grounded in the (private) knowledgebase and may leak unpublished
# research ideas, so the file is kept out of git entirely. CI persists it
# across runs via actions/cache (see .github/workflows/update-feed.yml).
data/llm_cache.json
